16:31.740 --> 16:34.780
they say that in the 16th century

16:34.780 --> 16:38.480
the wealthiest place in the world

16:38.480 --> 16:40.660
were China and Tuscany

16:41.800 --> 16:45.020
so I was not alive in that time

16:45.020 --> 16:47.540
but anyway I do trust

16:47.540 --> 16:48.960
I do trust historians

16:50.880 --> 16:54.560
but in this case the new China is different

16:54.560 --> 16:57.000
because the first time in history

16:57.000 --> 17:01.060
that a country has a new strategy

17:02.860 --> 17:05.260
operates in the world economy with goods

17:05.260 --> 17:08.480
selling goods that we buy every day

17:08.480 --> 17:10.140
exporting people

17:10.140 --> 17:11.820
emigrates everywhere

17:11.820 --> 17:15.060
in Africa, in Italy and so on

17:15.580 --> 17:18.440
but technology and capital together

17:18.440 --> 17:21.500
if you analyze the world history

17:21.500 --> 17:24.060
it never happened that a country could

17:24.640 --> 17:26.120
put together

17:27.020 --> 17:29.060
and it is incredible

17:29.060 --> 17:31.380
incredible because they did

17:31.730 --> 17:33.120
in the world scale

17:37.060 --> 17:40.180
6 years ago I was in Algeria

17:40.180 --> 17:41.620
asking Bouteflika

17:41.620 --> 17:43.780
what about Chinese?

17:44.520 --> 17:45.400
what about Chinese?

17:46.100 --> 17:47.820
I went out of Chinese

17:47.820 --> 17:49.960
and I told look professor

17:49.960 --> 17:53.020
we had the problem of social housing

17:53.020 --> 17:56.160
we needed to build social housing

17:56.160 --> 17:58.720
and the price of Chinese

17:58.720 --> 18:01.780
was half of the Italians and the French

18:01.780 --> 18:05.640
and so they came here 25,000 Chinese

18:05.640 --> 18:08.430
they delivered the houses

18:09.900 --> 18:12.660
as regular as a Swiss clock

18:12.660 --> 18:14.900
and you know

18:14.900 --> 18:16.600
and then what he had

18:16.870 --> 18:19.380
every year 5000 Chinese

18:19.930 --> 18:22.500
stop working and other come

18:22.500 --> 18:25.580
and get married here in Algeria

18:25.580 --> 18:27.540
and so we have a small entrepreneurship

18:27.540 --> 18:29.400
that I need so much

18:29.400 --> 18:32.920
2 years ago I asked how is going

18:33.200 --> 18:35.000
and he told me look

18:35.000 --> 18:37.480
as I told you 5 years ago

18:37.480 --> 18:40.180
but now we have already

18:40.180 --> 18:43.120
25,000 Chinese

18:43.120 --> 18:44.740
with Algerian citizenship

18:45.240 --> 18:47.080
you know this is

18:47.080 --> 18:49.580
when they are quicker to give

18:49.580 --> 18:51.200
Algerian citizenship

18:51.200 --> 18:53.580
than in Italy to give Italian citizenship

18:53.580 --> 18:56.580
certainly but the type of

18:57.160 --> 18:58.780
strategy is quite interesting

18:58.780 --> 19:00.280
and for the future

19:00.280 --> 19:02.680
it will change the world

19:02.680 --> 19:05.960
and clearly China

19:05.960 --> 19:07.660
