19:13.740 --> 19:16.900
but I only list them

19:16.900 --> 19:17.760
banks

19:21.640 --> 19:23.880
from the economic point of view

19:23.880 --> 19:27.300
banks and the overproduction

19:27.300 --> 19:29.240
of many traditional sectors

19:29.500 --> 19:31.500
from the political point of view

19:31.500 --> 19:34.140
is a strong

19:36.360 --> 19:39.020
political power struggle

19:39.020 --> 19:42.260
there is a real power struggle

19:42.260 --> 19:43.840
but

19:43.840 --> 19:45.900
and corruption

19:46.580 --> 19:50.800
and also a deep demographic problem

19:50.800 --> 19:53.480
because the one child policy

19:53.480 --> 19:56.620
