20:31.940 --> 20:33.180
in the middle of the century

20:33.180 --> 20:37.100
it's incredible this change of the world

20:38.780 --> 20:39.860
but

20:39.860 --> 20:41.660
and this is the point

20:41.660 --> 20:44.660
in order to

20:44.660 --> 20:48.220
let's say go on with the development

20:48.220 --> 20:51.120
power in China has been

20:52.240 --> 20:53.320
concentrated

20:54.020 --> 20:56.640
we have a more central power now

20:56.640 --> 20:58.400
that anytime

20:59.100 --> 21:00.680
after Mao Zedong

