21:12.540 --> 21:14.500
fight that is incredible

21:14.500 --> 21:17.720
if you analyze the Chinese

21:19.500 --> 21:21.820
analysts today

21:21.820 --> 21:24.060
consider that it would be between

21:24.060 --> 21:28.740
150,000 to 400,000 people

21:28.740 --> 21:30.160
under accusation

21:31.380 --> 21:32.260
incredible

21:32.260 --> 21:32.780
but

21:36.100 --> 21:39.060
is also an instrument

21:39.060 --> 21:41.480
to concentrate power

21:41.480 --> 21:44.600
and so now you have

21:44.600 --> 21:47.750
