22:23.040 --> 22:26.980
and it was in my knowledge the first time

22:26.980 --> 22:30.160
in many decades that United Kingdom

22:30.160 --> 22:33.800
made a policy different from United States

22:33.800 --> 22:36.060
because the interest

22:36.060 --> 22:37.800
to have the RMB

22:38.760 --> 22:42.520
